GAL20V8
U09

NC A0148 A1148 A2148 G5148 FC0 FC1 FC2 AS A1 A2 GND
A3 RESETIN NC IACK NC RESET NC IPL2 IPL1 IPL0 NC VCC

;EQUATIONS

; 1. Ciclo de IACK (Pino 16)
IACK = FC2 & FC1 & FC0 & !AS

; 2. Lógica dos IPLs (Pinos 20, 21, 22)
; Se IACK = 0 (Normal): Espelha o 74LS148
; Se IACK = 1 (Acknowledge): Mantém o último valor (Auto-realimentação)

!IPL2 = !A2148 & !IACK # !IPL2 & IACK
!IPL1 = !A1148 & !IACK # !IPL1 & IACK
!IPL0 = !A0148 & !IACK # !IPL0 & IACK

; 3. Reset Pass-through
RESET = RESETIN

DESCRIPTION
Buffer de interrupcao com trava de IACK para Orion68K.
